title: 184: R.I.C.E. - Rest, Ice, Compression, Elevate
description:
How many risks have you taken in 2019? How many risks have you taken in your life? Earlier this year Karl took some time to figure out what he wanted his life to look like outside of ETA and in 6 months he’s changed the trajectory of his life and his families life. ET and CJ interview Karl to get the blueprint on what he did to go from living a good life to living a phenomenal life. Karl emphasizes that if you truly desire to live a certain way and to have certain things you can make it a reality. Ask yourself today what is it that you really want and are you willing to work for it?
